title: The Bible Series - John Bevere - The Bait of Satan
description:
The Bible Series - John Bevere - The Bait of Satan


Angels Demons Nephilim and Aliens (Parts 1-4) by Rev. Jim Wilhelmsen:
Are angels physical beings? What are demons? How do the two relate to the Nephilim or Aliens. This video will answer these questions and more from the Bible using the Bible and not man made rhetoric.  Demons what are they and what do they have to do with the returning Nephilim from Genesis 6 Everything you need to know from the Bible. 

The Nephilim and the Gibbowr are they the same being? How do the Giants of Genesis 6 relate to Legends, Myths, History and Archeology of Giants. How does this tie into the hollow earth and the descendants of Cain who were sentenced to this area. Here is some evidence to consider.  The final part of the series is the Dark alliance of human and non-human entities that create the real Army of Darkness. There are Biblical patterns that can tell us who is behind all of this as Satan's counterpart to Christ. Compelling evidence shows many Prophetic events have already happened as recorded history but not understood for what they really are. Comprehensive all of the scriptures are presented here as evidence to consider
